{"tid":392704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆粗鬧內地生「支那人」  周竪峰：樂於成為以言入罪第一人","createTime":"2017-09-08T16:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T01:10:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":804,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed65337bc223656c2d9ee4f04655e99dedac207","tid":392704,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1007957/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1007957%2F&d=VLFlM22RuJ65twpqsCwclV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6e84297b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1007957%2F&h=4977a683\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1007957/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170908/_2017090817100514075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170908%2F_2017090817100514075.jpg&h=8ad0b487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上流傳片段指中大學生會前會長周竪峰，情緒激動地與內地生對罵，罵對方是「支那人」，事件引起社會及學界關注。周竪峰在個人Facebook表示：「我樂於成為在香港因罵支那而以言入罪第一人」。<br />\n<br />\n一群學生早前在中大民主牆前張貼「醜成這樣還學人搞港獨」的簡體字海報，周竪峰向一名內地生爆粗罵對方是「支那人」，又叫對方滾回中國，「講廣東話呀，支那人！講廣東話呀！香港地方你唔撚講廣東話?」。<br />\n<br />\n中大今午發聲明回應，指收到校內和校外人士針對短片的投訴，認為有學生使用「粗口辱華」，已經啟動程序展開調查，強調會嚴肅處理事件。"},{"pid":"345c581c7f4c93003474a0e512afb0bb97d19dfb","tid":392704,"uid":60148,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70faabb1a47afcde1da1dcf74c359c746a72e98","tid":392704,"uid":4942,"like":406,"dislike":0,"score":406,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"辱華？<br />\n<br />\n好撚白痴<br />\n<br />\n有無聽過係美國黑人話白人「白皮豬」會比人口誅筆伐？ 但中國有成13億人既強大民族，就脆弱到好似一個三歲孩童咁"},{"pid":"df1ea190bfc84bdc527b3116e9990f6eb25fcffd","tid":392704,"uid":38523,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"cit